{"name":"Alert the team on new events with Twilio 24/7 for Fulfillment","nodes":[{"parameters":{"httpMethod":"POST","path":"wf09154-order","options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.webhook","typeVersion":2,"position":[-270,400],"id":"7a6bdd73-fd46-466e-81d1-799954018398","name":"Receive Inbound Webhook","webhookId":"aa5daff4-3544-4351-9d44-c0c875310ec8"},{"parameters":{"assignments":{"assignments":[{"id":"a5555c4d-1882-432c-8e36-b12b20c13216","name":"orderId","value":"={{ $json.body?.orderId || $json.body?.id }}","type":"string"},{"id":"0af0871e-0f45-417f-b194-895ad2de9543","name":"kind","value":"={{ $json.body?.type || 'default' }}","type":"string"},{"id":"facc2b1e-1a03-4283-8154-4a3d09afb7ee","name":"payload","value":"={{ JSON.stringify($json.body || $json) }}","type":"string"}]},"options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.set","typeVersion":3.4,"position":[54,400],"id":"4fa0d752-ba6e-4923-bf36-1f0e26fb5793","name":"Map to Canonical Schema"},{"parameters":{"rules":{"values":[{"conditions":{"options":{"caseSensitive":true,"leftValue":"","typeValidation":"strict","version":2},"conditions":[{"id":"3b8a9fb7-3e3a-43c9-8dc1-dd815964bd5b","leftValue":"={{ $json.kind }}","rightValue":"opened","operator":{"type":"string","operation":"equals"}}],"combinator":"and"},"renameOutput":true,"outputKey":"opened"},{"conditions":{"options":{"caseSensitive":true,"leftValue":"","typeValidation":"strict","version":2},"conditions":[{"id":"ccee2041-d7dc-43f2-af29-d988ff109cb0","leftValue":"={{ $json.kind }}","rightValue":"closed","operator":{"type":"string","operation":"equals"}}],"combinator":"and"},"renameOutput":true,"outputKey":"closed"},{"conditions":{"options":{"caseSensitive":true,"leftValue":"","typeValidation":"strict","version":2},"conditions":[{"id":"42fbf0b5-1bb9-43a5-8b0c-2bfc57452a5e","leftValue":"={{ $json.kind }}","rightValue":"reopened","operator":{"type":"string","operation":"equals"}}],"combinator":"and"},"renameOutput":true,"outputKey":"reopened"}]},"options":{"fallbackOutput":"extra"}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.switch","typeVersion":3.2,"position":[378,400],"id":"9ce79542-1d39-4a84-bb2b-bbfdb0f5449b","name":"Route by Event Kind"},{"parameters":{"operation":"appendOrUpdate","documentId":{"__rl":true,"mode":"list","value":"","cachedResultName":"Order Tracker"},"sheetName":{"__rl":true,"mode":"name","value":"Main","cachedResultName":"Main"},"columns":{"mappingMode":"autoMapInputData","value":{},"matchingColumns":["orderId"],"schema":[]},"options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.googleSheets","typeVersion":4.7,"position":[702,130],"id":"c5a3ae7a-c9a2-4c76-a60b-1e08dd228303","name":"Handle 'opened' → Google Sheets","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000},{"parameters":{"method":"POST","url":"https://api.example.com/v1/orders","sendBody":true,"specifyBody":"json","jsonBody":"={{ JSON.stringify($json) }}","options":{"timeout":20000}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest","typeVersion":4.2,"position":[1026,640],"id":"b32d0051-edff-4034-8f5b-367a415885f5","name":"Handle 'closed' → Forward API","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000},{"parameters":{"method":"POST","url":"https://api.example.com/v1/orders","sendBody":true,"specifyBody":"json","jsonBody":"={{ JSON.stringify($json) }}","options":{"timeout":20000}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest","typeVersion":4.2,"position":[1350,1150],"id":"119abc7e-5678-47b3-b7df-e86a489adda8","name":"Handle 'reopened' → Forward API","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000},{"parameters":{"operation":"append","documentId":{"__rl":true,"mode":"list","value":"","cachedResultName":"Order Tracker"},"sheetName":{"__rl":true,"mode":"name","value":"Main","cachedResultName":"Main"},"columns":{"mappingMode":"autoMapInputData","value":{},"matchingColumns":[],"schema":[]},"options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.googleSheets","typeVersion":4.7,"position":[1674,1660],"id":"81bd4853-c7c8-46ea-9f11-eceef5f39ce8","name":"Log Unrecognized Kind","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000},{"parameters":{"mode":"append","numberInputs":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.merge","typeVersion":3.2,"position":[2322,400],"id":"8e4a09b6-aca2-4979-ad38-efd19ec88671","name":"Consolidate Handling"},{"parameters":{"respondWith":"json","responseBody":"={{ { \"ok\": true } }}","options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.respondToWebhook","typeVersion":1.1,"position":[3294,400],"id":"7017f455-a51d-47b1-9441-390e98d49c09","name":"Respond with Outcome"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Receive Inbound Webhook\n\nEntry point: listens for POST calls on `/wf09154-order`. Use the TEST url while building, switch callers to the PRODUCTION url after publishing.\n\nNext: Map to Canonical Schema","width":280,"height":232,"color":5},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-330,520],"id":"29782b8e-dc14-c029-58a5-0b5ebd840941","name":"Note: Receive Inbound Webhook"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Map to Canonical Schema\n\nShapes the item: writes `orderId`, `kind`, `payload`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Route by Event Kind","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-6,520],"id":"f88aa789-806e-051d-1a5c-b7631069c383","name":"Note: Map to Canonical Schema"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Route by Event Kind\n\nRoutes each item to one of 4 lanes: opened, closed, reopened + fallback.\n\nPorts: ①→ Handle 'opened' → Google Sheets · ②→ Handle 'closed' → Forward API · ③→ Handle 'reopened' → Forward API · ④→ Log Unrecognized Kind","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[318,520],"id":"ea0a6f1d-e82f-c8ea-ff16-23d009d58045","name":"Note: Route by Event Kind"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Handle 'opened' → Google Sheets\n\ngoogleSheets — `appendOrUpdate` operation against the connected account.\n\nNext: Consolidate Handling\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[642,250],"id":"3f429390-61a8-7c2e-05de-61d2c2f0689f","name":"Note: Handle 'opened' → Google Sheets"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Handle 'closed' → Forward API\n\nPOST https://api.example.com/v1/orders — retries 3× with backoff on failure.\n\nNext: Consolidate Handling\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 API key / bearer for the target API","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[966,760],"id":"8dc21690-ede6-d6cf-c92a-822d4cbd9f2d","name":"Note: Handle 'closed' → Forward API"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Handle 'reopened' → Forward API\n\nPOST https://api.example.com/v1/orders — retries 3× with backoff on failure.\n\nNext: Consolidate Handling\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 API key / bearer for the target API","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1290,1270],"id":"7c967c92-85cd-cb71-c597-5cd2d546fd75","name":"Note: Handle 'reopened' → Forward API"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Log Unrecognized Kind\n\ngoogleSheets — `append` operation against the connected account.\n\nNext: Consolidate Handling\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1614,1780],"id":"f3d31b14-ec84-01db-7516-f20831474bd8","name":"Note: Log Unrecognized Kind"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Consolidate Handling\n\nRejoins 4 branches into one stream (mode: append) so downstream logic runs once.\n\nNext: Respond with Outcome","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2262,520],"id":"ae61e360-5601-2102-0b55-4712cffbc595","name":"Note: Consolidate Handling"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Respond with Outcome\n\nSends the HTTP 200 response back to the caller — keep this fast; heavy work happens after/async.","width":280,"height":232,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3234,520],"id":"dacc8ebf-991e-5ccb-54cd-fec716c9820d","name":"Note: Respond with Outcome"},{"parameters":{"content":"# Alert the team on new events with Twilio 24/7 for Fulfillment\n\n**Pattern:** Event Notification · **Level:** Foundation · **Trigger:** Webhook\n\n## What it does\nAlert the team on new events with Twilio 24/7 for Fulfillment. It fires the moment an external system calls its webhook.\n\n## Why it exists\nManual fulfillment is slow and error-prone; this workflow makes the process repeatable, monitored and hands-off, with failures surfaced instead of silently lost.\n\n## Main flow\nReceive Inbound Webhook → Map to Canonical Schema → Route by Event Kind → Handle 'opened' → Google Sheets → Consolidate Handling → Respond with Outcome\n\n## Use it for\n- Teams that want to event notification without manual effort\n- Anyone automating fulfillment in e-commerce\n- Replacing a fragile manual process with a reliable workflow\n\n## You get\n- Removes copy-paste errors\n- Improves response time\n- Saves hours of manual work each week\n\n## Before first run\nConnect credentials: API key / bearer for the target API; Google OAuth2 / service account.\nFollow the color key: 🟦 entry · 🟪 AI · 🟫 actions · ⬜ utilities · 🟩 outputs · 🟥 error rail.\nEach node has its own doc card underneath — read those before editing.","width":480,"height":900},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-830,80],"id":"c2d6adb9-e211-b6cb-3ec2-249b331f1423","name":"📘 Workflow Overview"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🔐 Security\n\nNever trust inbound payloads: the webhook path is unguessable. Add header auth or IP allow-listing for defense in depth. Secrets live in n8n credentials — never in node parameters.","width":360,"height":260,"color":1},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-230,-290],"id":"3ff6aa0d-b700-9eab-bbf2-7acbb6febd05","name":"🔐 Security"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛠 Customize me\n\nQuick wins: point the data nodes at your own accounts (see 🔑 lines on each card), adjust the trigger cadence, and tune thresholds/labels to your fulfillment process. Every node card explains its role — safe to extend at any marked branch.","width":360,"height":260,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[190,-290],"id":"0ae9fb31-9508-4076-57c8-59250cab8c4f","name":"🛠 Customize me"}],"connections":{"Receive Inbound Webhook":{"main":[[{"node":"Map to Canonical Schema","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Map to Canonical Schema":{"main":[[{"node":"Route by Event Kind","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Route by Event Kind":{"main":[[{"node":"Handle 'opened' → Google Sheets","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Handle 'closed' → Forward API","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Handle 'reopened' → Forward API","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Log Unrecognized Kind","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Handle 'opened' → Google Sheets":{"main":[[{"node":"Consolidate Handling","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Handle 'closed' → Forward API":{"main":[[{"node":"Consolidate Handling","type":"main","index":1}]]},"Handle 'reopened' → Forward API":{"main":[[{"node":"Consolidate Handling","type":"main","index":2}]]},"Log Unrecognized Kind":{"main":[[{"node":"Consolidate Handling","type":"main","index":3}]]},"Consolidate Handling":{"main":[[{"node":"Respond with Outcome","type":"main","index":0}]]}},"active":false,"settings":{"executionOrder":"v1"},"meta":{"templateCredsSetupCompleted":false},"tags":[],"pinData":{},"versionId":"735e14c0-f9ca-45d0-a1a8-dc41741cdecd","id":"FDX09154"}